{"tid":811892,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚去左風俗店,咁樣係咪蝕左?","createTime":"2018-09-09T07:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T09:07:18.000Z","uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b08ab37dbd45ed3123a71be0906a85feb1582c2","tid":811892,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:59:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的,呢排去左日本<br />\n琴日屎忽痕想試下屌人屎忽<br />\n上網搵左間風俗店,<br />\n揀左個自稱廿幾歲個樣幾靚,個body幾健壯<br />\n佢黎到我間房幾有禮貌,問我想做咩先<br />\n<br />\n因為我唔係幾識日文,我就叫佢揸fit<br />\n一開波我地沖涼個陣,佢順手幫我全身洗乾淨<br />\n洗埋個屎眼,覺得有啲唔對路<br />\n我廢事比啲架仔以為我唔識野,冇理佢<br />\n事後先諗返佢冇洗佢自己屎眼<br />\n<br />\n佢一邊幫我打jer又玩我粒lin,間中打下車輪咁<br />\n之後佢搽完ky就隊左入黎,一邊un一邊chok J,好爽<br />\n事後佢係我銀包拎完錢就走左<br />\n諗諗下先覺得唔對路,<br />\n我冇屌到佢屎眼係咪蝕左?"},{"pid":"1d918c904f1c2f4682557110d4a3135f6ee34921","tid":811892,"uid":134665,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T08:01:03.000Z","msg":"黎明呢排好低質"},{"pid":"81cab73d38f5f09a7d5782527ca80bf3c4b7cadf","tid":811892,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1d918c904f1c2f4682557110d4a3135f6ee34921","tid":811892,"uid":134665,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T08:01:03.000Z","msg":"黎明呢排好低質"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"我黎明想知我係咪蝕左底"},{"pid":"93618e040868d840ba205f7d408c83cbb85fe541","tid":811892,"uid":134665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81cab73d38f5f09a7d5782527ca80bf3c4b7cadf","tid":811892,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1d918c904f1c2f4682557110d4a3135f6ee34921","tid":811892,"uid":134665,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T08:01:03.000Z","msg":"黎明呢排好低質"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"我黎明想知我係咪蝕左底"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T08:03:00.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"24ccbf4a15bc61155a1dd449ab7d5b045d8bace0","tid":811892,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93618e040868d840ba205f7d408c83cbb85fe541","tid":811892,"uid":13466